Document_summary: This document is an application for approval of a Power Purchase Agreement between Hawaiian Electric Company, Inc. and Kalaeloa Solar Two, LLC. It outlines the terms and conditions of the agreement, including the construction and interconnection of the solar photovoltaic energy facility, compliance with Hawaii's energy policies, and provisions for curtailment of energy delivery by Hawaiian Electric.

This document is an application by Hawaiian Electric Company seeking approval for a Power Purchase Agreement with Waiawa PV, LLC for a solar project in Hawaii. The document outlines the project details, requested approvals, and financial impacts. Time sensitivity is emphasized due to the project's construction milestones and the need for Commission approval by May 4, 2015.
